title: This Week in Highlights | 2/27/2017
description: Here's this week in highlights coming at you from NYC, Detroit, London, and Hamburg !! What a crazy week as you can see in DailyVee but if you're strapped for time this is the podcast for you, capturing all of this week's best clips, from fixing the well, not the sink - The meaning of winning - and what it means to "taste everything"
